[49m[38;5;10m+    214[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    215[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ## General Architecture Pattern
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    216[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    217[0m:[38;5;10m[49m A healthcare care coordination assistant decomposes into ten logical stages: enrollment and episode-of-care instantiation, longitudinal episode-of-care store management, cross-system status retrieval and reconciliation, coordination-gap detection and proactive engagement, channel entry, input safety screening with continuous emergency screening, identity-and-context loading, conversation handling with action-versus-ask policy enforcement, output safety screening, and care-team reporting with outcome tracking. The cross-cutting concerns from recipes 11.1 through 11.8 carry forward; this recipe adds five new ones (multi-system integration governance, coordination-rules-engine ownership by clinical and care-management leadership, action-versus-ask policy enforcement, records-transfer orchestration with cross-modality coverage, and cross-provider consent posture enforcement).
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    218[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    219[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ```
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    220[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── ENROLLMENT + EPISODE-OF-CARE INSTANTIATION ────┐
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    221[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    222[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Patient enrolled by institution per episode trigger]   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    223[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Care-team identifies patient as appropriate for      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    224[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      coordination support (cancer diagnosis, surgical     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    225[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      workup, post-discharge transition, complex specialty │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    226[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      referral, multi-specialty workup)                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    227[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Episode-of-care template selected per the            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    228[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      institutional library (oncology, surgery, transition │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    229[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      from inpatient, post-procedure recovery, etc.)       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    230[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Episode instantiated with patient-specific values:   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    231[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      involved providers, care plan, expected milestones,  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    232[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      coordination dependencies, escalation criteria       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    233[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Patient reviews and consents to coordination         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    234[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      assistance                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    235[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Cross-provider consent posture configured            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    236[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           │                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    237[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           ▼                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    238[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Output: signed consent record; episode-of-care record;│
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    239[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    longitudinal store initialization]                     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    240[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    241[0m:[38;5;10m[49m └───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    242[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    243[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── LONGITUDINAL EPISODE-OF-CARE STORE ────────────┐
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    244[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    245[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Patient-assistant longitudinal store]                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    246[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Active episodes of care (one or more)                │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    247[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Per-episode care-plan reference                      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    248[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Per-episode involved providers                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    249[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Per-episode milestones (completed, in flight,        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    250[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      pending, blocked)                                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    251[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Per-episode referrals with statuses                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    252[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Per-episode orders (lab, imaging, prescriptions)     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    253[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      with statuses                                        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    254[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Per-episode insurance authorizations with statuses   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    255[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Per-episode records-transfer events with statuses    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    256[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Per-episode appointments (past, upcoming)            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    257[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Cross-provider consent posture                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    258[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Stated patient preferences (channels, quiet hours,   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    259[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      language, preferred name, caregiver authorization)   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    260[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Conversation history                                 │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    261[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Coordination-gap detection state                     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    262[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    263[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Storage architecture]                                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    264[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Structured data: DynamoDB tables                     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    265[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Conversation transcript: S3 with vector retrieval    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    266[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Episode timeline: structured events with             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    267[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      cross-system reconciliation logic                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    268[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           │                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    269[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           ▼                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    270[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Output: longitudinal store ready for coordination]     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    271[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    272[0m:[38;5;10m[49m └───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    273[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    274[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── CROSS-SYSTEM STATUS RETRIEVAL ─────────────────┐
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    275[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    276[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Integrated source systems]                             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    277[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - EHR (institutional, often multiple across providers) │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    278[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Health Information Exchange (HIE)                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    279[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Institutional scheduling system                      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    280[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Referral-management system                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    281[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Lab and imaging order-tracking systems               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    282[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Prior-auth tracking system                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    283[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Patient-portal messaging system                      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    284[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Direct Trust messaging infrastructure                │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    285[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - FHIR endpoints for institutionally-connected         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    286[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      providers                                            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    287[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Care-management workflow system                      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    288[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    289[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Retrieval pipeline]                                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    290[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Per-system authentication (institutional IdP, OAuth, │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    291[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      federated identity for cross-institutional)          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    292[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Per-system retrieval with rate-limiting and          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    293[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      error-handling                                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    294[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Cross-system reconciliation (the same referral may   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    295[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      have different statuses in different systems)        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    296[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Data freshness tracking                              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    297[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Stale-data warnings                                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    298[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           │                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    299[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           ▼                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    300[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Output: unified cross-system view of the patient's    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    301[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    coordination state]                                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    302[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    303[0m:[38;5;10m[49m └───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    304[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    305[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── COORDINATION-GAP DETECTION ────────────────────┐
